        <!-- =====================================================================
             SHARED PATTERNS / GLASS BOX  (y=800 - 1020)
             ===================================================================== -->
        <mxCell id="shared_band" value="SHARED PATTERNS — applied to every agent" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;fillColor=#f8fafc;strokeColor=#475569;strokeWidth=1.5;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=6;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#0f172a" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="30" y="800" width="1860" height="225" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="sp1" value="🛡  Glass Box audit pattern&#10;&#10;Every agent calls the reusable Log_To_Audit child flow&#10;→ writes ONE row to Decision_Rationale per decision.&#10;&#10;Row contents: agent, input_hash, output, confidence, model, latency_ms, claim_id.&#10;&#10;This single table satisfies CO SB21-169, NAIC, NY DFS, CA AB 2930." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef3c7;strokeColor=#d97706;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#92400e;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="50" y="838" width="440" height="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="sp2" value="⚡  Parallel execution&#10;&#10;Master_Orchestration uses Power Automate parallel branches:&#10;• Extraction · Policy · Validation run concurrently (~30 s wall time vs ~90 s serial)&#10;• Each branch independently writes its audit row&#10;• Join step waits for all 3, then calls Adjudication&#10;&#10;Per-agent timeouts: 45 s with 2 retries (exponential back-off)." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dbeafe;strokeColor=#0078d4;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#0a2540;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="510" y="838" width="440" height="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="sp3" value="🔒  Failure handling + human-in-the-loop&#10;&#10;• Any agent timeout or error → audit row with status='error' → escalate to Tier 2&#10;• Adjudication low-confidence (&lt; 0.85) → Tier 2 Teams Adaptive Card to adjuster&#10;• Fraud / fatality / total-loss / distressed-sentiment → Tier 3 live CSR chat&#10;• Tier 2 + Tier 3 human decisions ALSO logged to Decision_Rationale (agent='human_adjuster' / 'human_csr')" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fee2e2;strokeColor=#dc2626;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#7f1d1d;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="970" y="838" width="900" height="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- =====  FOOTER KEY  ===== -->
        <mxCell id="footer" value="KEY:  Purple = Microsoft Copilot Studio / Power Automate  ·  Blue = Azure AI  ·  Gold = Glass Box audit  ·  Red dashed lines = audit writes / reads  ·  Orange = customer-facing  ·  Each agent's audit row makes its decision auditable, explainable, and regulator-ready." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;fontColor=#5a6680" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="30" y="1040" width="1860" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

